WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:21.839
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:34.199
For it reaches to the highest mountain. Those are communion cups from the last couple times.

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:40.486
I have to start picking up my stuff a little bit more. Oh, there it goes.

00:00:40.487 --> 00:00:55.838
All four. Bummer. Is anybody here? Yeah. Father, I plead the blood of Jesus.

00:00:55.839 --> 00:01:01.519
Thank you, Father, for your angels that watch over us tonight as we pray.

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:06.594
Thank you, Father, that we only pray with your heart, no flesh.

00:01:06.595 --> 00:01:29.799
Thank you, Lord. We go right into the throne, Lord. Ready? Good evening, family.

00:01:29.800 --> 00:01:38.439
How are y'all doing today? I just wanted to come on tonight and pray with you for a little bit.

00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:46.329
Last night when we prayed, we prayed really late to reach other parts of the world, but my heart was to pray for Australia.

00:01:46.330 --> 00:02:02.116
We prayed for Australia, Africa, and New Zealand. The Lord was showing us a great revival coming to Australia, a fresh, new, mighty outpouring of the Spirit of God.

00:02:02.117 --> 00:02:14.959
Then I was seeing new songs; new heavenly songs are going to start to come forth. The Lord was telling us to pull on that.

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:27.610
If you are a person that makes music and writes music, I believe there's going to be heavenly music given to you as you press into the Father.

00:02:27.611 --> 00:02:34.995
You're not seeking fame or finances, but you're seeking just to worship.

00:02:34.996 --> 00:02:41.268
I believe the Lord doesn't care if we have blessings, as long as the blessings don't have us.

00:02:41.269 --> 00:02:47.119
I want you to know that's what the Lord was showing us: that there are new heavenly songs coming.

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:53.229
There are songs that we've never heard before that are going to be glorious.

00:02:53.230 --> 00:03:07.759
Beautiful music is coming, and I would expect it right now. As we were praying last night, we saw the power grid again.

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:26.898
As President Trump starts doing these tariffs and sanctions, the Lord showed me attacks against the power grid: Los Angeles, the Bay Area, Chicago, and New York—these places of great populations.

00:03:26.899 --> 00:03:38.879
The Lord told us last night we need to pray against power outages concerning cyber attacks and cyber warfare.

00:03:38.880 --> 00:03:54.559
I don't know who would be taking care of our power grid—maybe our army or whoever is over the cyber division—to have supernatural wisdom on how to combat the attacks that are coming.

00:03:54.560 --> 00:04:07.437
I believe they've already started. I saw Trojan horses coming in and causing disruption in our power grid in America in a greater way.

00:04:07.438 --> 00:04:20.712
It would not just be a couple of hours of power outage; we're talking a sustained amount of power being out for maybe days.

00:04:20.713 --> 00:04:25.879
I'm not trying to stir up fear; I'm trying to tell you it's something you should be prayerful about.

00:04:25.880 --> 00:04:38.600
Every single thing I bring to you is to bring prayer over our nation and for our president, for Homeland Security, the FBI, and the CIA.

00:04:38.601 --> 00:04:50.208
I just believe that there's power in prayer. Just as we saw that the man in Atlanta was going to try to do a mass shooting there and he was stopped by the authorities.

00:04:50.209 --> 00:05:00.935
All glory to God. There was confusion in the camp, and that's what we pray: that they don't have their thoughts right when they're trying to do things like that.

00:05:00.936 --> 00:05:09.125
He went in and his family told on him, and then all of a sudden the authorities said they believed that he was going back.

00:05:09.126 --> 00:05:15.844
He was scoping out the area and going back to his truck to get whatever he was going to get to hurt people.

00:05:15.845 --> 00:05:35.177
I believe this is what we're called to do. We're assembling together tonight to stop Satan's plans. Principalities work through personalities.

00:05:35.178 --> 00:05:50.037
Weak-minded people who already have a reprobate mind and are not strong in the Word are coming in, and they're trying to grab a hold of these people that already have yielded themselves over to demonic influence.

00:05:50.038 --> 00:06:05.336
We want to pray for a hedge of protection around our sporting events, including the World Series that starts tomorrow, Friday.

00:06:05.337 --> 00:06:15.199
We pray over the World Series; it's best out of seven. We are praying over our college events and any kind of major event: Thanksgiving, Black Friday, and all these things.

00:06:15.200 --> 00:06:38.215
We are praying over our economy and for President Trump. As he said, he's putting more sanctions on Russia and their oil companies, so we know what will happen with that.

00:06:38.216 --> 00:06:50.120
I just believe this situation—you try to put people in a corner by touching their pocketbook—but I've seen an escalation of things.

00:06:50.121 --> 00:06:59.782
I heard one pastor say, 'Oh, Brandon, we're going to stop war altogether.'Well, that goes against Matthew 24.

00:06:59.783 --> 00:07:11.209
I'm going to line up with the Word, not with what you think. The Bible said we would have wars and rumors of wars.

00:07:11.210 --> 00:07:26.700
We'll have plagues, pestilences, and famines. This is the beginning of sorrows, and I believe we're in that timeframe.

00:07:26.701 --> 00:07:33.980
No matter how much we try to stop it, you're not going to stop the Bible.

00:07:33.981 --> 00:07:39.668
The Bible stands alone, and there is no prophetic word that's going to go against the Word of God.

00:07:39.669 --> 00:07:46.918
If it goes against the Word of God, it's not God and it's not a prophetic word; it's a false word, a false prophecy.

00:07:46.919 --> 00:07:58.319
We know what's coming, ladies and gentlemen. The Lord said to me today while I was outside, 'Brandon, there's not enough urgency.

00:07:58.320 --> 00:08:14.113
Again, you must tell My people I'm coming again. You must tell them that they need to have a sense of urgency about My coming.'I went over what I said to you all yesterday.

00:08:14.114 --> 00:08:24.537
Every time I go over everything I've said to you because I don't want any prophetic confusion.

00:08:24.538 --> 00:08:34.999
I've said a thousand times, and Paul Begley and others say, 'Brandon, you're called to be like a prophet,'but I always say I'm a watchman and I believe I have a prophetic lens.

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:39.733
I'm able to see, and the Lord said, 'Your main focus is to bring prayer to YouTube.

00:08:39.734 --> 00:08:46.878
I want you to bring a massive prayer audience. I want a million-man and woman prayer army.

00:08:46.879 --> 00:08:57.599
As you pray, you will change things and you will protect what's coming.'If they don't know Psalm 91 and Psalm 23, they're in trouble.

00:08:57.600 --> 00:09:05.687
Is that to scare you? No, it's to prepare you. You must know the Word of God. You must understand your covenant.

00:09:05.688 --> 00:09:25.016
I know there are a lot of Word of Faith people who believe we're not going to go through anything, saying, 'Well, brother, as long as we're the salt, we're holding back the Antichrist.'I believe wholeheartedly that we are the salt and the restrainer because the Holy Ghost is in us.

00:09:25.017 --> 00:09:29.279
Some people believe we're going to go through the whole tribulation. I do not.

00:09:29.280 --> 00:09:36.042
I believe that we're not appointed unto wrath, and I believe with all my heart that we'll be taken out of here before all that mess starts.

00:09:36.043 --> 00:09:45.519
But it's not the beginning of sorrows, and I believe we're going to see some things before the Great Tribulation begins.

00:09:45.520 --> 00:09:53.136
That's just me. I believe some of the other people in my circle believe the same way.

00:09:53.137 --> 00:09:57.910
I'm telling you what I feel inside my spirit: the beginning, the birthing pains.

00:09:57.911 --> 00:10:05.402
As labor pains upon a woman, so will it be. I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, we're going to see some stuff.

00:10:05.403 --> 00:10:15.199
The Lord told me about what the word was, Braden. I want to say the exact word.

00:10:15.200 --> 00:10:29.116
He said, "I'm putting in my closers."And closers are built for pressure.

00:10:29.117 --> 00:10:38.959
Great pressure is coming. You must have a sense of urgency. What's the C-word, Braden?

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:55.087
I've said it a thousand times today, and my mind, when I get on these live streams, just kind of goes.

00:10:55.087 --> 00:11:00.838
Obviously, we need to write this stuff down when He gives us these words because it's not our vocabulary.

00:11:00.839 --> 00:11:05.167
So, just knowing that we have to be that person with the backbone, with the crowbar.

00:11:05.168 --> 00:11:12.175
I'm trying to tell you all, the Lord's been talking to me outside while I've been cleaning and doing the things I've been doing.

00:11:12.176 --> 00:11:20.079
He said, "You must come at this stronger, for the great harvest of souls is ahead.

00:11:20.080 --> 00:11:36.254
For many are called, but few are chosen, for the harvest is plentiful and the labors are few."That's why I'm having the urgency of saying, Braden, having the closer.

00:11:36.255 --> 00:11:48.859
Where we are right now in this dispensation, we're about to enter into the dispensation of judgment, but we're in grace for just this little bit of a window left.

00:11:48.860 --> 00:11:56.101
Right now, He's calling forth His church to have some urgency to bring in the harvest.

00:11:56.102 --> 00:12:16.374
That's why I was trying to tell you all yesterday, not that I was knocking having a hundred souls born again or having a few people getting born again, but I said, "Where is the church having major mass revival?"The Lord said to me, "Brandon, I'm waiting on the souls.

00:12:16.375 --> 00:12:45.479
I'm leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one."That's why I was pushing in, saying, "Lord, anoint me with a special anointing, whatever it takes to bring in the harvest like a Billy Graham in these last days to bring in the lost."If 170-some thousand people die daily and you only get a hundred people born again, I don't feel like that's great numbers.

00:12:45.480 --> 00:12:55.920
Even if we all got a hundred people saved, we need millions of people to get saved.

00:12:55.921 --> 00:13:02.279
I believe it's going to come through a great shaking to awaken.

00:13:02.280 --> 00:13:07.679
Every time I pray this, He says, "Brandon, that's why I'm bringing the shaking.

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:17.959
Everything is going to be about a change within a 24-hour period."He keeps talking about a major change within a 24-hour period.

00:13:17.960 --> 00:13:22.881
A major shaking is coming. Everything that we've ever known will change.

00:13:22.882 --> 00:13:33.559
When we went to the 23rd of September, He told me, "Brandon, after this timeframe, a great acceleration will come.

00:13:33.560 --> 00:13:49.950
A great acceleration will come from the 23rd of September, from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah."He said, "Remember, as labor pains upon a woman, we see the acceleration and it's going."He said, "This would be the time of the point of no return.

00:13:49.951 --> 00:13:56.500
It's time for the push."When I say the point of no return, I'm talking about whenever a woman can get an epidural.

00:13:56.501 --> 00:14:00.445
There's only a certain time of the labor that you can get an epidural.

00:14:00.446 --> 00:14:19.214
But the Lord said to me, "Brandon, we are at that point right now of the push, as labor pains, to be contenders."We must be contenders.

00:14:19.215 --> 00:14:26.948
We must fight for what's ours. You can't lay down and just feel sorry for yourself. The Lord said, "Brandon, I'm putting in the fighters.

00:14:26.949 --> 00:14:42.825
How bad do you want the outpouring of the Spirit of God on this last generation?"You think the devil's going to sit by and not try to put up a wall to restrain this or try to stop it?

00:14:42.826 --> 00:14:55.445
You're going to have to contend for it. You're going to have to have a bulldog-on-a-bone type of personality that says, "I'm the one that's going to make it upstream. I'm the salmon that's going to make it upstream.

00:14:55.446 --> 00:15:26.599
I'm going to be the one that witnesses into this earth."That's why He said, "For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few."As I observe church services and look at the pulse—and I'm not trying to pick at anybody, I'm telling you through the prophetic lens of what I'm praying over—where's the urgency in the church?

00:15:26.600 --> 00:15:45.838
People say, "Well, Brandon, you're too harsh."As you drive down the road, the only way I can describe this to you is you can see the ones that are truly successful, the business owner versus the one that works for the one who owns the business.

00:15:45.839 --> 00:15:56.855
Your mentality has to change, thinking bigger for these end times. How big of a soul harvest are you believing for?

00:15:56.856 --> 00:16:07.114
If I just get one saved, folks, you've got to think bigger than that. The Lord said, "Brandon, believe bigger.

00:16:07.115 --> 00:16:36.804
I wish that none should perish, but all come to repentance."What if we had all the people who've ever been saved for the last 2,000 years all saved within a couple of years?

00:16:36.805 --> 00:16:42.479
Greater works will you do. Think bigger. But what will it take?

00:16:42.480 --> 00:16:48.300
Money. It takes finances. How much money does it take to get the gospel out?

00:16:48.301 --> 00:16:54.919
Just for TV time, it takes millions of dollars. Believe big.

00:16:54.920 --> 00:17:01.399
He's exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think. And the Lord taught me it's time to expand your capacity.

00:17:01.400 --> 00:17:07.759
You need to think bigger for what I'm about to do in this end-time army.

00:17:07.760 --> 00:17:14.584
You're thinking too small. If I could believe God for a million dollars, that's a lot to me.

00:17:14.585 --> 00:17:35.318
But the Lord said, "You're thinking too small, Brandon."I thought, "Wow."For somebody who made minimum wage all their life, a million dollars will change your life.

00:17:35.319 --> 00:17:43.239
But to somebody who's already a multimillionaire, they look at it and say, "Braden, a million dollars ain't nothing."But to somebody who hadn't had nothing, that's a lot.

00:17:43.240 --> 00:17:49.091
And the Lord said, "You need to think bigger."That's why I drove through West Palm Beach.

00:17:49.092 --> 00:17:56.839
He said, "Look at Billionaire Road. Enlarge your capacity to believe Me.

00:17:56.840 --> 00:18:03.678
Think different."So when I was looking at the souls, that's what I was trying to tell you all.

00:18:03.679 --> 00:18:14.719
When I was looking at the souls and things, you see Rodney Howard-Browne, he has big altar calls, and you see Billy Graham, but you don't see a lot of people having big altar calls anymore.

00:18:14.720 --> 00:18:23.659
Very seldom do you even see anybody—I go to a lot of churches and you don't see very many altar calls with even one or two people getting saved.

00:18:23.660 --> 00:18:30.930
I thought that's a shame. There has to be more. Because that's what He said when He's touching the doorknob.

00:18:30.931 --> 00:18:45.851
I looked at Him in the vision and I saw Jesus, and He said, "I'm waiting on My Father's instruction to tell Me to come and get you."And I asked the Father, and it was thunderous.

00:18:45.852 --> 00:18:52.678
He said, "Brandon, you help Me bring in the harvest and I'll come and get you.

00:18:52.679 --> 00:19:09.479
That's all you're waiting on is a major outpouring."So I thought, "What brings in the harvest?"My mind has just been turning because once you've experienced the glory one time—I'm not picking at anybody, but I'm looking for authentic.

00:19:09.480 --> 00:19:11.918
People say they've been to heaven, they've done this, they've done that.

00:19:11.919 --> 00:19:16.359
I'm looking for authentic. I want the presence when you're talking.

00:19:16.360 --> 00:19:23.904
If you say you've seen my Father, if you say you've seen my Jesus, is there a presence on you when you talk about it?

00:19:23.905 --> 00:19:29.849
Because when I'm telling you what I've been in front of, in his presence there's fullness of joy.

00:19:29.850 --> 00:19:39.759
In his presence, there's fullness of love. And I'm telling you, the glorious church will rise out of it.

00:19:39.760 --> 00:19:45.439
When you say you have an impartation from my Father, there should be fruit.

00:19:45.440 --> 00:19:49.985
I want to see fruit. I don't want to just hear words. I don't want to hear just a story.

00:19:49.986 --> 00:19:59.199
I want to see the glory. And I believe the people who walk with him are going to display glory.

00:19:59.200 --> 00:20:10.071
When you say that, I want to see glory on your face. I want to look upon his face.

00:20:10.072 --> 00:20:24.519
With one touch, with one breath, it'll change you forever. When you just behold his face, it will change you forever.

00:20:24.520 --> 00:20:31.734
You'll never be the same. A real radical touch from Jesus; you'll never be the same.

00:20:31.735 --> 00:20:40.439
It's that fire that never burns out; it's the water that never runs dry. Do you understand?

00:20:40.440 --> 00:20:51.510
And when you say you've seen him—whenever I've seen somebody who's authentically had an encounter with him, because I believe I have—it changes you.

00:20:51.511 --> 00:21:04.599
It makes you hungry. It makes you desperate. There's nothing more that you want other than just to get away from this world and go, 'How can I be with you?'There's nothing more.

00:21:04.600 --> 00:21:23.159
I don't care who you are. One touch, one drink, and you'll become addicted. Other than that, I question if you're authentic or not.

00:21:23.160 --> 00:21:32.319
I question you because I know when you touch it and you drink it, it changes you forever.

00:21:32.320 --> 00:21:37.434
And that's whenever he tells me, and I see it and I had these experiences with him.

00:21:37.435 --> 00:21:42.519
He says, 'Brandon, I'm coming.'And I'm like, 'There's nothing I want more.

00:21:42.520 --> 00:21:52.074
You couldn't offer me a fleet of Ferraris. You couldn't offer me a fleet of yachts. Jesus is all you want.

00:21:52.075 --> 00:22:05.279
Once you taste the glory, once you taste his presence, once you look upon his face, once you look into his eyes, there's nothing more you ever want.

00:22:05.280 --> 00:22:10.799
I remember he looked at me and he said, 'Brandon, are you willing to die for me?

00:22:10.800 --> 00:22:23.079
Are you willing to lay down your life for the cause if I ask you to?'Oh God, you ask so much.

00:22:23.080 --> 00:22:28.390
But yes, of course, whatever it takes to get this gospel out, Lord.

00:22:28.391 --> 00:22:50.079
Charlie Kirk, no matter how you get the threats, how many people try to come against you and tell you they want to hurt you, they want to do things to you, I have a family to protect, but at the same time, I know that all the disciples died other than one by martyrdom.

00:22:50.080 --> 00:22:54.929
What did it take to get the gospel out 2,000 years ago? What pressure?

00:22:54.930 --> 00:23:05.689
How much of a sacrifice? Why were they so radical? They had walked with him. They had been with him for three years. Do you understand?

00:23:05.690 --> 00:23:15.839
Once they tasted the glory, once they experienced the presence of God, they were willing to lay everything down for the cause of Christ.

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:24.119
That's somebody who's truly seen him and truly been with him because there's nothing else that matters.

00:23:24.120 --> 00:23:29.853
I try to tell you all this because there's coming a point in time that the pressure is coming.

00:23:29.854 --> 00:23:37.611
He said the olive pressure—like olives—he said the pressure is coming on my church, Brandon, and the oil will flow.

00:23:37.612 --> 00:23:55.079
A new Holy Ghost oil will flow, but it's coming out of pressure in Canada, in America, in England, China, Europe, South America.

00:23:55.080 --> 00:24:04.678
Most people are in La La Land. They don't look at what's coming.

00:24:04.679 --> 00:24:10.372
And he told me a great shaking's coming, and most people don't want to hear it.

00:24:10.373 --> 00:24:15.639
I caught wind of some of this last week. We don't want to hear that.

00:24:15.640 --> 00:24:21.559
Well, you need to hear it because it's coming whether you like it or not.

00:24:21.560 --> 00:24:28.239
You're not going to stop it. I told you you must pray; a plague's coming.

00:24:28.240 --> 00:24:36.119
I told you a plague worse than COVID on steroids is coming. Most people don't want to hear that.

00:24:36.120 --> 00:24:40.559
Am I trying to scare you? No. I'm trying to prepare you way in advance.

00:24:40.560 --> 00:24:49.814
Does it have to affect you in your house? No. Do you hear me? No. What is Psalm 91?

00:24:49.815 --> 00:25:03.359
'A thousand shall fall at my side and ten thousand at my right hand, but it will not come nigh me.'No pestilence, no plagues, no nothing will come nigh me.

00:25:03.360 --> 00:25:11.559
Psalm 23: 'Though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death, I will fear no evil.

00:25:11.560 --> 00:25:22.639
Why? Because his rod and his staff comfort me. He prepares a table before me in the presence of all my enemies.

00:25:22.640 --> 00:25:31.599
My cup runneth over. Surely goodness and mercy follow me.'I just believe that God's able to do what he said he would do.

00:25:31.600 --> 00:25:49.279
And when you become fully persuaded like Abraham, I'm fully persuaded that what God has promised, he's able also to perform it.

00:25:49.280 --> 00:25:57.479
And he said he'd give his angels charge over me to bear me up in their hands, lest I dash my foot against a stone.

00:25:57.480 --> 00:26:07.719
So I'm not afraid of any plagues. To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord regardless of where I'm at in life.

00:26:07.720 --> 00:26:15.039
I still believe a thousand bullets fall at my side and ten thousand on my right hand, but nothing shall come nigh me, my wife, and my children.

00:26:15.040 --> 00:26:26.559
I anoint my head with oil, my cup runneth over. Surely goodness and mercy follow me. I just believe that he is my provider.

00:26:26.560 --> 00:26:42.599
And regardless of economic crisis, regardless of what I've told you, a 1930s-style crash is coming—one worse than what we had before 100 years ago.

00:26:42.600 --> 00:26:52.959
'Oh, Brandon, now you're really freaking me out.'I said one that's worse than you can ever comprehend is what I have seen multiple times as I pray.

00:26:52.960 --> 00:27:05.895
But the Lord said, 'Brandon, I'm giving you a window for a financial blessing for my people who prayed last year at this time when we were interceding for the election.'He said, 'I'm giving you a longer window.

00:27:05.896 --> 00:27:20.568
I'm giving you a space of time to get your house in order, to get your boat ready for a major shaking to awaken is coming.'And that's what's been stirring in me today.

00:27:20.569 --> 00:27:34.633
I've been praying over it, interceding for the harvest. He said, 'For I'm bringing a shaking to awaken for a harvest, for they're all asleep.'Most of my church and most people go, 'Well, I don't believe that.

00:27:34.634 --> 00:27:40.639
I'm charismatic.'Are you the only one in the church? Why is it always about the charismatics?

00:27:40.640 --> 00:27:47.079
Why is it always about the Word of Faith people? We're the church. You're blind and you're full of pride.

00:27:47.080 --> 00:27:52.115
There's Baptists, there's Methodists, there's Catholics, there's Church of Christ.

00:27:52.116 --> 00:28:01.959
They all love the Lord. They just have different doctrine than you do.

00:28:01.960 --> 00:28:09.266
I'm trying to tell you there's all kinds of believers and God is calling all of us to be assembled as one body.

00:28:09.267 --> 00:28:24.833
And he said, 'I'm bringing down all the tents and you will operate as one body, radically born again, excited about my soon return.'And it's not going to be, 'Well, I speak in tongues, you don't; you're Catholic, this'—I mean them all.

00:28:24.834 --> 00:28:30.239
But I'm going to tell you what we all have in common is we love Jesus.

00:28:30.240 --> 00:28:35.854
That's why I say I don't like religion; I just want a relationship. And people get upset about that.

00:28:35.855 --> 00:28:40.204
'Why did you say you don't like religion?'Because religious tents—this is what I'm talking about.

00:28:40.205 --> 00:28:49.199
'Well, you're this, you're that'—who cares. Let's just have a heart for Jesus.

00:28:49.200 --> 00:28:59.954
I said a great shaking is coming to the Catholic Church, a radical shaking, and there will be a great revival.

00:28:59.955 --> 00:29:15.831
And then he showed me that he was correcting the LDS and a great shaking was coming to the LDS and there would be a splitting of the church.

00:29:15.832 --> 00:29:22.239
And he said he's correcting wrong doctrine, for it's a cult.

00:29:22.240 --> 00:29:49.879
